@UrlShortener_HostAddress = http://localhost:5025
@ContentType = application/json

### 🟢 Get all shortened URLs
GET {{UrlShortener_HostAddress}}/api/Urls
Accept: application/json

###

### 🟢 Get a specific URL mapping by ID
GET {{UrlShortener_HostAddress}}/api/Urls/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 🟢 Create a new shortened URL
POST {{UrlShortener_HostAddress}}/api/Urls
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "longUrl": "https://www.microsoft.com",
  "customShortCode": "msoft",          // optional
  "expirationUtc": "2025-12-31"  // optional
}

###

### 🟢 Update an existing shortened URL
PUT {{UrlShortener_HostAddress}}/api/Urls/1
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "longUrl": "https://www.updatedexample.com",
  "expirationUtc": "2026-01-01"
}

###

### 🟠 Delete a shortened URL
DELETE {{UrlShortener_HostAddress}}/api/Urls/1

###

### 🟢 Redirect test (simulate visiting the short URL)
GET {{UrlShortener_HostAddress}}/r/msoft
